marc21:datafield.marc21:subfield: 21 x 17 cm. (sheets); 26 x 16 cm. (queen regent stationery cover)

196 pages and cardboard notebook cover labeled "Queen Regent Stationery." <br>Entries record Beaux's daily activities, including regular notes on her work in the studio and with various sitters for portraits, social events, her health, her correspondence, and people she saw. <br>Almost all entries are typewritten but a few are written by hand.
Archives of American Art, Smithsonian Institution
